---
// Hero — Stripe 체계 벤치마크 적용 (타이포·리듬·CTA·웨이브)
// 색상은 하우스맨 네이비 유지 (Apple/Stripe 복제 X)
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-hero-blobs">
  <div class="hero-wave"></div>

  <div class="relative container-narrow py-section grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center">
    <!-- 좌 7 — 메시지 -->
    <div class="md:col-span-7">
      <p class="eyebrow mb-5">
        <span class="inline-block w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-navy-700 mr-2 align-middle"></span>
        HOUSEMAN OS · 건물 운영체제
      </p>

      <h1 class="font-display text-display-xl text-ink">
        당신 건물의<br/>
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-navy-900 via-navy-700 to-navy-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          운영체제.
        </span>
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-6 text-body-l text-ink-body max-w-[560px]">
        당신 건물 스타일 그대로, 하우스맨이 시스템으로 짜 드립니다.<br/>
        15년 현장 경험 + <strong class="text-navy-700">하우스맨 OS</strong>로 건물별 맞춤 세팅.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-9 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
        <a href="/onboarding" class="btn-primary">
          셋업 견적 받기 <span class="text-sm font-normal opacity-80">(3분 질문지)</span>
          <span class="text-base">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="tel:1544-4150" class="link-arrow text-base">
          무료 상담 1544-4150 →
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- 신뢰 지표 인라인 -->
      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap gap-6 text-sm text-ink-body">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="font-bold text-ink">100+</span>
          <span class="text-ink-label">관리 건물</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="font-bold text-ink">1,100+</span>
          <span class="text-ink-label">호실</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="font-bold text-ink">800+</span>
          <span class="text-ink-label">부동산 네트워크</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="font-bold text-ink">15년</span>
          <span class="text-ink-label">경력</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 우 5 — 알림톡 비주얼 (Stripe UI 목업 자리 차용) -->
    <div class="md:col-span-5 relative h-[460px] hidden md:block">
      <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 w-full space-y-4">
        <div class="alertkakao-card delay-0">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1.5">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-yellow-400"></span>
            <span class="text-[11px] font-bold text-ink-label tracking-wider">[하우스맨]</span>
            <span class="text-[11px] text-ink-label ml-auto">방금</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink leading-relaxed">
            역삼101호 월세 <strong class="text-navy-700">85만원</strong> 청구서가 도착했습니다.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="alertkakao-card delay-1">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1.5">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-yellow-400"></span>
            <span class="text-[11px] font-bold text-ink-label tracking-wider">[하우스맨]</span>
            <span class="text-[11px] text-ink-label ml-auto">1분 전</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink leading-relaxed">
            역삼101호 <strong class="text-navy-700">납부 완료</strong>가 확인되었습니다.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="alertkakao-card delay-2">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1.5">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-yellow-400"></span>
            <span class="text-[11px] font-bold text-ink-label tracking-wider">[하우스맨]</span>
            <span class="text-[11px] text-ink-label ml-auto">방금</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink leading-relaxed">
            금월 정산 리포트 PDF가 이메일로 발송되었습니다.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .alertkakao-card {
    @apply bg-white text-ink rounded-card-lg p-4 shadow-mockup border border-ink-line
           opacity-0 translate-y-4;
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
    .alertkakao-card {
      animation: slide-in 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.2, 1, 0.2, 1) forwards;
    }
    .alertkakao-card.delay-0 { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
    .alertkakao-card.delay-1 { animation-delay: 1.4s; }
    .alertkakao-card.delay-2 { animation-delay: 2.4s; }
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .alertkakao-card { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
  }
  @keyframes slide-in {
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
</style>
